OL,3,CMinister visits Hawick to launch new
OL,4,CSouth of Scotland Housing Action Plan
OL,6,FHousing Minister Paul McLennan MSP has
OL,7,Fvisited a site in Hawick to launched
OL,8,Fthe new South of Scotland Housing
OL,9,FAction Plan.
OL,11,FThe plan was launched at Burnfoot
OL,12,Fwhere the Scottish Borders Housing
OL,13,FAssociation is currently building 16
OL,14,Fnew homes across two sites.
OL,16,FIt aims to tackle the need for more
OL,17,Fhomes in the region by increasing the
OL,18,Fprovision of affordable housing.
