OL,6,FIt also hopes to attract more people
OL,7,Fto work and live in the area, grow the
OL,8,Flocal construction sector, and create
OL,9,Fnew student and key worker
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FThis follows Scottish Borders Council
OL,13,Frecently declaring a housing emergency
OL,14,Fin the area.
