OL,3,CMinister visits Hawick to launch new
OL,4,CSouth of Scotland Housing Action Plan
OL,6,FCouncillor Euan Jardine, the leader of
OL,7,FScottish Borders Council said: "Whilst
OL,8,FScottish Borders Council has an
OL,9,Fexcellent record of working with our
OL,10,Flocal partners to develop additional
OL,11,Fhousing, particularly affordable
OL,12,Fhomes, it is essential for the future
OL,13,Fof the South of Scotland that we do
OL,14,Fall we can to address the housing
OL,15,Fneeds of our residents and support
OL,16,Fexisting businesses and further inward
OL,17,Finvestment.
