OL,3,CMinister visits Hawick to launch new
OL,4,CSouth of Scotland Housing Action Plan
OL,6,F"The Action Plan does more than just
OL,7,Ftarget the building of new homes
OL,8,Fthough, with a focus also on skills
OL,9,Fand supporting the construction sector
OL,10,Fwhich will be essential to ensuring
OL,11,Fthat growth continues long into the
OL,12,Ffuture."
OL,14,FIt's predicted that more than 9,000
OL,15,Fnew homes maybe needed in the next ten
OL,16,Fyears in the South of Scotland.
OL,18,FWork on the ten point action plan is
OL,19,Fexpected to be carried out over the
OL,20,Fnext two years.
