OL,3,CMinister visits Hawick to launch new
OL,4,CSouth of Scotland Housing Action Plan
OL,6,FMr McLennan said: "The South of
OL,7,FScotland Housing Action Plan and the
OL,8,Fpartnership work that underpins it is
OL,9,Fa key step in our collaborative
OL,10,Fresponse to the housing pressures
OL,11,Ffacing the region.
OL,13,F"As recognised in the plan, housing
OL,14,Fplays an important role in promoting
OL,15,Feconomic growth and is a key enabler
OL,16,Fto making the change that we want to
OL,17,Fsee in our rural and island economies.
OL,26,@nD@SOUuD@AOU
