OL,3,CMinister visits Hawick to launch new
OL,4,CSouth of Scotland Housing Action Plan
OL,6,F"Across the local authorities within
OL,7,Fthe South of Scotland we will make
OL,8,Favailable over #27million from the
OL,9,FAffordable Housing Supply Programme in
OL,10,F2024-25, helping to deliver much
OL,11,Fneeded affordable homes.
OL,13,F"We remain committed to delivering
OL,14,F110,000 affordable homes across
OL,15,FScotland by 2032, of which at least 70
OL,16,Fper cent will be for social rent and
OL,17,F10 per cent in rural and island
OL,18,Fcommunities.
